/*
Imp Points 
1. Node.js is not a programming language,technology,framework,library
2. It is Javascript runtime environment.

[Js se backend nahi ban skta, kyuki js ke paas wo functionalities nahi hai jinse backend banta hai]

Ryan dahl ne socha js se backend banna chahiye,Google chrome ka v8 enginer ka code open source hai and ryan dahl us code mein chhedkhaani kar raha hai.

Fir Ryan dahl ne socha ki humein to js mein code krna hai, and chrome ka v8 enginer bana hai c++ mein.

Hum js ka code likhenge jo ki wrapper layer of js receive karega and wo code v8 enginer ke c++ modules ke saath ek server create karega.

Node.Js == v8+ Js

*/